      "**Multi-adapter serving is the unlock**: base loaded once + many swappable adapters routed per tenant; S-LoRA/Punica batch across adapters → N customers ≈ one model's GPU cost.",
      "**Adapters are first-class artifacts**: version, A/B, hot-swap per request, instant rollback by re-pointing the router — no 140GB redeploy.",
      "**Merge only for single-tenant/latency-critical** — merging rebuilds a full model copy and kills hot-swap/rollback; multi-tenant keeps adapters separate.",
