          "The right next step is preference alignment on (chosen, rejected) pairs, via DPO's pairwise loss or RLHF's reward-model-plus-PPO pipeline",
          "More SFT will fix it — adding another 5,000 examples of the single best answer per prompt teaches the model to prefer that answer over alternatives",
